import Head from "next/head";

const Meta = () => (
  <Head>
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#da532c" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/static/favicon_alveo.png" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/static/favicon_alveo.png" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/static/manifest.json" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/static/Alveo-Logo.png" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:300,400&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/_fonts-import.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/_slick.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/_slick-theme.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles/_antd.css" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/static/styles/_react-image-gallery.css" />
  </Head>
);

export default Meta;
